<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Appointment Update Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #dc3545;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .appointment-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
      background-color: #fff3cd;
    }
    .appointment-details strong {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Appointment Update</h2>
    <p>Hello {{ patientName }},</p>
    <p>Your appointment has been updated by Dr. {{ doctorName }} with the following details:</p>
    <div class="appointment-details">
      <p><strong>New Status:</strong> {{ status }}</p>
      {{#if doctorNote}}
      <p><strong>Doctor's Note:</strong> {{ doctorNote }}</p>
      {{/if}}
      <p><strong>Appointment Time:</strong> {{ appointmentTime }}</p>
      <p><strong>Appointment Date:</strong> {{ appointmentDate }}</p>
    </div>
    <p>Please review your updated schedule and contact the clinic if you need further assistance.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Clinic Appointment System</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
